Package edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2013.brickus.iface

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BrickusListener
    This interface must be implemented by any class whose objects are called when Brickus model events occur.
    BrickusModel
    Classes implementing this interface declare that they are capable of serving as a standard Brickus model.
    BrickusPiece
    Implemented by classes which may represent a Brickus piece.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BrickusEvent
    Contains information pertaining to a Brickus model event.
    BrickusIllegalMoveEvent
    This event is raised byb a BrickusModel whenever a caller attempts to make an illegal move.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Player
    This enumeration represents the players in a game of Brickus.
